          <head>
            <note type="contents-note">This manuscript contains: Portions of the first half of a Choir-book, comprising the Psalms, according to the Peshitta version. In total, including sub-sections, this manuscript contains 1 items.</note>
            <listRelation type="Wright-BL-Taxonomy">
              <relation name="dcterms:type" ref="http://purl.org/dc/terms/type" active="https://bl.syriac.uk/ms/983" passive="#psalter">
